# UI / Console Rules

Framework constraints:
- Keep HTMX + server-rendered partials; no SPA frameworks.
- No progress bars by default; logs are the progress surface.

Console behavior:
- Preserve attach modes (STARTED vs ATTACHED / quiet attach).
- Preserve WebSocket + NOTIFY-based streaming.

Styling:
- Single CSS file.
- Terminal palette, sharp edges.
- Minimal animation.
